==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Usufruct
<hw>U"su*fruct</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>usufructus</ets>, <ets>ususfructus</ets>, <ets>usus et
fructus</ets>; <ets>usus</ets> use + <ets>fructus</ets> fruit.]</ety>
<fld>(Law)</fld> <def>The right of using and enjoying the profits of an
estate or other thing belonging to another, without impairing the
substance.</def> <rj><au>Burrill.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Usufructuary</ent>⟦br⟧
